# Java Calculator

A simple menu-driven calculator built in Java using the Scanner class.

## Features

- Addition
- Subtraction
- Multiplication
- Division
- Modulus
- Power
- Square Root
- Exception Handling

## Technologies

- Java
- OOP
- Scanner Class
- Exception Handling

## How to Run

Compile:

```bash
javac *.java
```

Run:

```bash
java Main
```
